Task Management System (Full Stack)

A production-style full stack Task Management System built using FastAPI, PostgreSQL, and React.
This project demonstrates secure authentication, role-based access control, scalable architecture, and modern frontend practices.

ðŸ“Œ Overview

This application allows users to register, authenticate securely using JWT, and manage tasks through a full CRUD interface.
Admins can manage all users and tasks, while normal users can manage only their own tasks.

The project follows industry backend architecture, secure coding practices, and modern React development patterns.

Architecture

